  <rdf:Description rdf:about="http://ontology.amt.org/codes/industries#demoId">
    <rdfs:comment>Form-level question identifier. Identifies which demographic question on the registration form this code answers. Multiple CodeElements within the same CodeSet may share a demoId (multiple answers per question); demoId may also vary across elements when industry-related answers are spread across multiple form questions.</rdfs:comment>
